  "texts": [
    "Taxonomic classes of Insecta, Actinopterygii, Aves, and Mammalia were over-represented classes in our dataset, each with >150 effect sizes from >30 studies (Supplementary Fig. 2).",
    "We thus created four separate meta-regressions for each class, with ejaculate trait as a moderator.",
    "Moreover, four species: lab mice (Mus musculus), lab rats (Rattus norvegicus), chicken/red junglefowl (Gallus spp.",
    "), and bulls (Bos taurus) were over-represented in our dataset (each species had >150 effect sizes across >20 studies; Supplementary Fig. 2).",
    "For these species, we created separate meta-regression models with ejaculate trait as a moderator."
  ],
